# @sfcr/web testing

- Tests live in `packages/web/test/`, not colocated with `src/`.
- Default iteration: `pnpm web:test:fast` (excludes four `App.notebook-*.test.tsx`).
- Notebook source/navigation/assistant/cell editors: `pnpm web:test:integration`.
- Focused run: `pnpm --filter @sfcr/web exec vitest run test/Foo.test.tsx --reporter=dot`
- DOM tests: `// @vitest-environment jsdom` at top of file.

Worker testing:
- Prefer `handleWorkerRequest` directly (`workerHandler.test.ts`).
- For `Worker` global: `vi.stubGlobal("Worker", MockWorker)` (`workerClient.test.ts`, `useSolver.test.tsx`).
- App integration: reuse `appTestUtils.tsx` mocks.

Prefer `@sfcr/core` imports over deep `../../core/src/...` paths in new tests.
